1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 14=

4
00:00:17,519 --> 00:00:18,199
Dasheng.

5
00:00:19,079 --> 00:00:20,320
This osmanthus pastry is really sweet.

6
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,120
You have it.

7
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:22,960
You can't get it anywhere else.

8
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:23,559
Come on, just try it.

9
00:00:23,559 --> 00:00:24,280
No, I don't want any.

10
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,079
Just try it.

11
00:00:27,199 --> 00:00:28,160
You do realize

12
00:00:28,519 --> 00:00:30,519
we're running for our lives, right?

13
00:00:30,519 --> 00:00:31,679
I know.

14
00:00:31,679 --> 00:00:32,159
You do?

15
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,719
Look at all this stuff we bought.

16
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:36,119
Do we look like
we're running for our lives?

17
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:40,079
Then I should get a few more waterskins.

18
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:41,479
We'll need them while we're on the run.

19
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,000
That...

20
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,799
That's the carriage of Su Yeye,

21
00:01:09,799 --> 00:01:11,640
the top courtesan at Zhenqu Pavilion,
Jinling's finest pleasure house.

22
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:14,879
They say even a fortune
can't buy a meeting with her.

23
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:16,519
She's famously aloof.

24
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:17,959
That smells wonderful.

25
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,319
What's so wonderful about it?

26
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,120
It's just perfume and powder.

27
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,519
Let's go.

28
00:01:41,879 --> 00:01:43,040
Mr. Peng.

29
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,000
I'm Su Yeye.

30
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,000
Would you join me in the carriage?

31
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,400
Miss, you know me?

32
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:56,319
Ever since the martial tournament
at Murong Manor,

33
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,959
your name has spread throughout
the martial world.

34
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:02,439
Who doesn't know you now?

35
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,799
My young master
is busy running for his life.

36
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:05,599
He doesn't have time for this.

37
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:08,240
Why such a hurry?

38
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,280
Are you eloping

39
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,400
with the young lady beside you?

40
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:11,960
I...

41
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,520
Xiaojiu,

42
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:17,080
I'll see what she wants.

43
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:17,800
Wait here.

44
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,639
I won't be long.

45
00:02:19,599 --> 00:02:20,719
All right.

46
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:23,280
But be careful.

47
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:52,639
Mr. Peng, why don't you sit closer?

48
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:10,719
Just tell me what you want.

49
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,280
Excuse me, sir.

50
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:27,800
Did anyone pass by here just now?

51
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:32,159
Was he dressed all in white?

52
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,039
That's him.

53
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:07,080
(Mr. Peng,
if you refuse to obey the Master,)

54
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:09,520
(those close to you will pay the price.)

55
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:10,800
Dasheng,

56
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:14,199
what did that flirt say?

57
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,360
Nothing.

58
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,800
It's getting late.

59
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:19,759
We need to keep moving.

60
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,399
The old master of Huxiao Manor

61
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,480
returned home yesterday.

62
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,600
He was overcome with rage

63
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,560
and died soon after.

64
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,720
The Lin family
just finished the funeral today.

65
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,879
Huxiao Manor
has terrorized people for years

66
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,720
and committed every evil imaginable.

67
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,920
Looks like karma
finally caught up with them.

68
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,839
Sir! Sir!

69
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:39,839
Sir!

70
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,920
Keep following me,

71
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,439
and I'll break your legs.

72
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,639
Are you all right?

73
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,120
You're able-bodied.

74
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:04,639
Why lower yourself for a man like that?

75
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,959
I've done odd jobs for the Lin family
since I was a child.

76
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:08,160
It's all I can do.

77
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,399
My younger sister came down
with dysentery earlier this year.

78
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,480
She's been bedridden ever since.

79
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,560
We ran out of food long ago.

80
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,240
Without the Lin family's wages,

81
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:17,000
my whole family will starve.

82
00:05:26,079 --> 00:05:26,800
Sir, what's this for?

83
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,319
It's for you.

84
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,439
I can't accept it.

85
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,319
Take it.

86
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,480
We're leaving Gusu soon anyway.

87
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:40,839
Let's go.

88
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,680
Sir...

89
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:49,240
There's something
I'm not sure I should say.

90
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,040
What is it?

91
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,720
I heard Miss Murong has been bedridden

92
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:56,639
since the martial tournament.

93
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,879
She's sick?

94
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,800
A servant from the estate said

95
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,839
she's fallen ill from heartache.

96
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,839
I still need to buy
my sister's medicine,

97
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:07,120
so I should get going.

98
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,839
Dasheng,

99
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,399
why are you spacing out?

100
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:18,680
The sun will set if we don't leave.

101
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:20,600
It's nothing. Let's go.

102
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,040
Taiping Villa isn't far from here.

103
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,720
If we hurry,

104
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,360
we can still leave Gusu before dark.

105
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:38,959
Xiaojiu,

106
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,759
do you really mean that?

107
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:46,319
Dasheng,
it's written all over your face.

108
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,240
You were so distracted just now
that you could barely keep up.

109
00:06:49,759 --> 00:06:52,519
Besides, you and Miss Murong
were engaged, after all.

110
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:54,160
Clear the air and put her mind at ease.

111
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:55,399
She might feel much better.

112
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:58,319
Then you can get back on the road
without worrying.

113
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:58,879
Right?

114
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,959
Xiaojiu...

115
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:01,920
All right, all right.

116
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,800
Quit stalling.

117
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,959
Wait any longer,
and they may close the estate gates.

118
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,000
Let's go.

119
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,480
Go.

120
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:18,399
Sir, it's done.

121
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:22,160
Keep a close watch on Taiping Villa.

122
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,720
No one but Peng Dasheng

123
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,959
is allowed near it today.

124
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:28,439
Yes, sir.

125
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,480
Sir,

126
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,879
my sister is gravely ill,

127
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,680
and my mother is old and confused.

128
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,959
Please spare them.

129
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:40,959
Don't worry.

130
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,319
Once this is over,

131
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:45,040
I'll let them go.

132
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,160
Go.

133
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:56,900
(Taiping Villa)

134
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,519
And you are?

135
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,399
I'm Peng Dasheng.

136
00:08:12,399 --> 00:08:13,759
I heard Miss Murong was ill,

137
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:14,560
so I came to see her.

138
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:18,000
Mr. Peng, estate rules require you

139
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,160
to leave your blade here
before entering.

140
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:25,160
Xiaojiu, wait here.

141
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,160
I won't be long.

142
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,160
Okay.

143
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,840
Miss Murong?

144
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:15,639
Miss Murong?

145
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,679
She's been poisoned.

146
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,679
It's Bone-Eroding Poison.

147
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:56,879
Good thing the pills Master gave me
can keep the poison in check.

148
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,919
Then I can use my inner force
to draw the poison out of the sore.

149
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,399
That should do it.

150
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,320
So hot...

151
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,240
So hot...

152
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,159
Uh... um...

153
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,120
Miss Murong...

154
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,080
This isn't proper.

155
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,799
No, no.

156
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:34,279
Stop. Stop.

157
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:34,879
Wait, Miss Murong.

158
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:35,480
You can't do this.

159
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,240
You can't, Miss Murong.

160
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,480
This isn't proper.

161
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:38,720
No, no.

162
00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:39,639
So hot...

163
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,799
No, this isn't proper.

164
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,600
This isn't proper.

165
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:44,320
Miss Murong...

166
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,440
Miss Murong, stop moving.

167
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:48,480
Once Bone-Eroding Poison
spreads through your body,

168
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:49,919
not even an immortal can save you.

169
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,519
(How could he be here?)

170
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:54,080
(No.)

171
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,960
(The poison
must be making me see things.)

172
00:10:57,759 --> 00:10:59,159
(What is he doing?)

173
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:00,720
(Is he)

174
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,840
(going to...?)

175
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,519
Forgive me.

176
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,039
I've drawn out all the poison.

177
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,000
Rest for two more days,
and you'll be fine.

178
00:12:14,039 --> 00:12:15,240
That's Master's gu bee.

179
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:17,639
It's circling like a star.

180
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:19,200
Master is sending us a message.

181
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,559
Then why didn't
Master come tell us in person?

182
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,080
Come on. Let's go see.

183
00:12:44,279 --> 00:12:46,720
Let go of me! Let me go!

184
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:48,080
Xiaojiu!

185
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:56,180
♪Come on♪

186
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:01,380
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

187
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:06,300
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

188
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:09,500
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

189
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:12,580
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

190
00:13:12,980 --> 00:13:15,580
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

191
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:19,060
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

192
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:22,300
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

193
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:25,380
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

194
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:28,300
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

195
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:32,180
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

196
00:13:32,220 --> 00:13:35,220
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

197
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:40,900
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

198
00:13:41,300 --> 00:13:43,340
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

199
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:46,420
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

200
00:13:47,140 --> 00:13:49,540
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

201
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:53,340
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

202
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:56,060
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

203
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:59,100
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

204
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:02,540
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

205
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:06,860
♪I am my own king♪

206
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:21,500
♪I emerge into the world♪

207
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:23,260
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

208
00:14:23,260 --> 00:14:24,620
♪My pride is my trump card♪

209
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:26,420
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

210
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:27,820
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

211
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:29,580
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

212
00:14:29,580 --> 00:14:31,100
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

213
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:32,820
♪I dare to break every rule♪

214
00:14:32,820 --> 00:14:34,140
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

215
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:35,980
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

216
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:37,220
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

217
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:39,460
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

218
00:14:39,460 --> 00:14:40,980
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

219
00:14:40,980 --> 00:14:42,580
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

220
00:14:42,580 --> 00:14:44,180
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

221
00:14:44,180 --> 00:14:45,900
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

222
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:47,620
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

223
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:48,980
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

224
00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:50,620
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

225
00:14:50,620 --> 00:14:52,100
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

226
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,820
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

227
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:55,420
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

228
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:56,980
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

229
00:14:56,980 --> 00:15:01,300
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

230
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:03,460
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

231
00:15:03,460 --> 00:15:06,060
♪Let me write the legend♪

232
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:13,500
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

233
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:16,820
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

234
00:15:16,820 --> 00:15:19,300
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

235
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:23,380
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

236
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:26,340
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

237
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:28,820
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

238
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:31,860
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

239
00:15:31,860 --> 00:15:36,900
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
